{"tid":1150133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇番1983年嘅MV 真係覺得好唏噓","createTime":"2019-05-11T15:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T05:47:18.000Z","uid":200120,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f657ed20399777357c508b64599412dcd2cf5444","tid":1150133,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:28:55.000Z","msg":"在東方有粒珍珠閃閃發光<br />\n細個已經識得哼呢句<br />\n今日第一次睇哂成個MV<br />\n1983年嘅人可能期待過香港會愈變愈好<br />\n但2019年今日嘅人反而充滿絕望淨係想移民<br />\n就連班學生都要自殺<br />\n學生時期係最快樂嘅時候<br />\n但偏偏要承受折磨最後崩潰選擇解脫<br />\n今時今日香港咁差 最大責任一定係香港政府管理不善<br />\n不過依家我哋係解決唔到<br />\n唯一可以做到係好少好少<br />\n得把口同個KEYBOARD 但至少可以鼓勵香港人鼓勵自己人<br />\n文化承傳係靠人而唔係乜乜政策破壞到<br />\n希望香港人可以團結起來<br />\n願明天香港 也是天堂<br />\n定能看得見 一點曙光<br />\n這點光不是天上降下，而係每個人的生命火花<br />\n聚起來就是一圑火，温暖又奪目<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jvUYsHMIJC4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjvUYsHMIJC4&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=31efc879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jvUYsHMIJC4</a>"},{"pid":"1015f47855fedb7f52999eea4ab9d143aec4a04f","tid":1150133,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"39a6f8c088db16adafbfd82c6d441562a7398a08","tid":1150133,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:34:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0214a4a4f24679fd1d706f0b342431754b4e0e47","tid":1150133,"uid":223044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8f4e509a6264330b7da2ed126ee64fa6078475","tid":1150133,"uid":118120,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"以前面向國際既香港係充滿希望<br />\n今日面向大陸既香港...."},{"pid":"a266b22d176df94f2a931bb0a1dc7a47d9011438","tid":1150133,"uid":92356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"